    BackgroundImage: {fileID: -2441277322969603615, guid: 5d833bbe5effc5245b8c8e5380102d6f, type: 3}
  - <ID>k__BackingField: 82315d37-f628-4d6f-8616-90d4f90ee766
    <Name>k__BackingField: DialogueName3
    <Choices>k__BackingField:
    - <Text>k__BackingField: New Choice
      <NodeID>k__BackingField: 24e57c24-a0c0-49a1-9b90-8914e9525123
    <GroupID>k__BackingField: 
    <Position>k__BackingField: {x: 1748.8, y: 67.2}
    <Text>k__BackingField: Secondly, global capitalism and growing income also meant
      that more people in China are able to travel. In certain cases, being exposed
      to another country also deepens one's fascination for the culture of that country,
    <Actions>k__BackingField: []
    <LeftSprites>k__BackingField:
    - {fileID: 6800915032177342135, guid: 97dbcf3c2e2539d489c7150e0fe63bd8, type: 3}
    <RightSprites>k__BackingField: []
    <IsChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <IsRememberChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <RememberSO>k__BackingField: {fileID: 0}
    ChoiceSO:
    - {fileID: 0}
    BackgroundImage: {fileID: -2441277322969603615, guid: 5d833bbe5effc5245b8c8e5380102d6f, type: 3}
  - <ID>k__BackingField: 24e57c24-a0c0-49a1-9b90-8914e9525123
    <Name>k__BackingField: DialogueName4
    <Choices>k__BackingField:
    - <Text>k__BackingField: New Choice
      <NodeID>k__BackingField: de7b3002-5558-482a-b306-0fbd192081ec
    <GroupID>k__BackingField: 
    <Position>k__BackingField: {x: 2551.2, y: 67.2}
    <Text>k__BackingField: In the context of South Korea, the case of "Seoul syndrome"
      recently amongst China's youth where they suffer intense nostalgia and homesickness
      for South Korea has been noted to deepen the China's youth fascination for
      South Korean culture, especially idol culture.
    <Actions>k__BackingField: []
    <LeftSprites>k__BackingField:
    - {fileID: 6800915032177342135, guid: 97dbcf3c2e2539d489c7150e0fe63bd8, type: 3}
    <RightSprites>k__BackingField: []
    <IsChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <IsRememberChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <RememberSO>k__BackingField: {fileID: 0}
    ChoiceSO:
    - {fileID: 0}
    BackgroundImage: {fileID: -2441277322969603615, guid: 5d833bbe5effc5245b8c8e5380102d6f, type: 3}
  - <ID>k__BackingField: d4ce026e-1625-41ea-9e6c-7e4dc07edb22
    <Name>k__BackingField: DialogueName
    <Choices>k__BackingField:
    - <Text>k__BackingField: New Choice
      <NodeID>k__BackingField: 52b55f11-856a-434f-94a1-02ea6f61c8e6
    <GroupID>k__BackingField: 
    <Position>k__BackingField: {x: 179.2, y: 64}
    <Text>k__BackingField: Firstly, as Kpop culture becomes more popular in China,
      women's demand for them also increase as well especially when their purchasing
      power also increases which in turn leads to stronger export for the soft kind
      of masculinity
    <Actions>k__BackingField: []
    <LeftSprites>k__BackingField:
    - {fileID: 6800915032177342135, guid: 97dbcf3c2e2539d489c7150e0fe63bd8, type: 3}
    <RightSprites>k__BackingField: []
    <IsChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <IsRememberChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <RememberSO>k__BackingField: {fileID: 0}
    ChoiceSO:
    - {fileID: 0}
    BackgroundImage: {fileID: -2441277322969603615, guid: 5d833bbe5effc5245b8c8e5380102d6f, type: 3}
  - <ID>k__BackingField: de7b3002-5558-482a-b306-0fbd192081ec
    <Name>k__BackingField: DialogueName5
    <Choices>k__BackingField:
    - <Text>k__BackingField: New Choice
      <NodeID>k__BackingField: 5d7ac371-347b-4aba-b624-a0b5d01d1074
    <GroupID>k__BackingField: 
    <Position>k__BackingField: {x: 3275.2, y: 67.2}
    <Text>k__BackingField: Hence, in the context of China, rising income and greater
      access to travelling, in the case to South Korea, also further spurs the exportation
      of South Korea idol culture in China, which also leads to higher demand for
      the soft and effeminate mascilinity in China
    <Actions>k__BackingField: []
    <LeftSprites>k__BackingField:
    - {fileID: 6800915032177342135, guid: 97dbcf3c2e2539d489c7150e0fe63bd8, type: 3}
    <RightSprites>k__BackingField: []
    <IsChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <IsRememberChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <RememberSO>k__BackingField: {fileID: 0}
    ChoiceSO:
    - {fileID: 0}
    BackgroundImage: {fileID: -2441277322969603615, guid: 5d833bbe5effc5245b8c8e5380102d6f, type: 3}
  - <ID>k__BackingField: 5d7ac371-347b-4aba-b624-a0b5d01d1074
    <Name>k__BackingField: DialogueName6
    <Choices>k__BackingField:
    - <Text>k__BackingField: New Choice
      <NodeID>k__BackingField: a75698be-2a23-4c6e-9f20-41eb6c7826a6
    <GroupID>k__BackingField: 
    <Position>k__BackingField: {x: 3990.4, y: 76.799995}
    <Text>k__BackingField: 'Lastly, growing income has also been noted to have a
      strong correlation with demand for beauty products in China '
    <Actions>k__BackingField: []
    <LeftSprites>k__BackingField:
    - {fileID: 6800915032177342135, guid: 97dbcf3c2e2539d489c7150e0fe63bd8, type: 3}
    <RightSprites>k__BackingField: []
